\c 16
\s Ilizwe elanikwa isizwe sakoEfrayimi
\p
\v 1 Kwasekuphuma inkatho yabantwana bakoJosefa kusukela eJordani eJeriko, kusiya emanzini eJeriko ngempumalanga, inkangala isenyuka isuka eJeriko entabeni yeBhetheli\x + 8.15; 18.12,13.\x*;
\v 2 yasiphuma eBhetheli isiya eLuzi\x + Gen. 28.19.18.13. Hlu. 1.23,26.\x*, yadlulela emngceleni wamaAriki eAtarothi\x + 2 Sam. 16.10. 1 Lan. 27.33.\x*,
\v 3 yehlela entshonalanga emngceleni wamaJafilethi, isiya emngceleni weBhethi-Horoni ngaphansi\x + 16.5; 10.10.\x*, kwaze kwaba seGezeri\x + 16.10; 10.33.\x*; lokuphuma kwayo kwakuselwandle.
\v 4 Ngakho abantwana bakoJosefa, uManase loEfrayimi, balidla ilifa\x + 17.14.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Lomngcele wabantwana bakoEfrayimi ngokwensendo zabo wawu\add nje\add*: Ngitsho umngcele welifa labo empumalanga wawuyiAtarothi-Adari\x + 18.13; 16.2,7; 1 Lan. 2.54.\x* kuze kufike eBhethi-Horoni ngaphezulu\x + 16.3.\x*.
\v 6 Umngcele wasuphumela elwandle, eMikimethathi enyakatho\x + 17.7.\x*; lomngcele waphendukela empumalanga eTanathi-Shilo\x + 18.1.\x*, wedlula empumalanga usiya eJanowa;
\v 7 wasusehla usuka eJanowa usiya eAtarothi leNahara, wagudla iJeriko, waphumela eJordani\x + 1 Lan. 7.28.\x*.
\v 8 Kusukela eTapuwa umngcele waya entshonalanga\x + 12.17; 17.8.\x* esifuleni iKana\x + 17.9.\x*, lokuphuma kwawo kwaba selwandle. Leli yilifa lesizwe sabantwana bakoEfrayimi ngokwensendo zabo.
\v 9 Lemizi eyayehlukaniselwe abantwana bakoEfrayimi yayiphakathi kwelifa labantwana bakoManase, yonke imizi lemizana yayo\x + 17.9.\x*.
\v 10 Kodwa kabawaxotshanga elifeni amaKhanani ayehlala eGezeri\x + Hlu. 1.29. 1 Kho. 9.16. Josh. 15.63. 17.12,13.\x*. Ngakho amaKhanani ahlala phakathi kwabakoEfrayimi kuze kube lamuhla, ayesebenza njengezibhalwa\x + Gen. 49.15.\x*.